@kyrasedgwickofficial for @abcgma3 in one of my favorite designers ever @lapointe 

Kyra and I have been obsessed with these @byfar_official gold boots. The trick with a statement shoe is to make the rest of the look a level 10 in French girl effortless—let the shoes do all the work. A saturated silk shift dress fits the bill—anything too fitted or designed will compete. I also like keep jewelry to a minimum at morning shows, heavy metal (like the music) has no place in the AM. I want to keep things smooth, creamy and happy like the cup of coffee viewers have while watching. 

Glam: @girl__please @edwardcruz 

Thank you: @alexirae__ @ghosttailor @thehoneymanagency @ashleyfalcon @jessigoi @stylebyleora_
